# Complex Task — Demo First

Referenced from `AGENTS.md`.

When a task is complex (new architecture, unfamiliar APIs, multi-screen flows, significant UX decisions):

1. Launch sub-agents to research best practices and current SwiftUI patterns
2. Build a **minimal demo** that proves the approach
3. Present the demo to the user for review
4. Proceed to full implementation only after user approval

Do not implement the full solution silently when the approach is uncertain or high-risk.